WEBVTT

00:00:05.132 --> 00:00:06.860
Please tell me you speak English.

00:00:08.469 --> 00:00:10.766
I’m Detective Carter!

00:00:10.804 --> 00:00:13.204
Do you speaka any English?

00:00:16.542 --> 00:00:20.536
Do you understand the words
that are coming out of my mouth?

00:00:25.919 --> 00:00:28.410
I cannot believe this shit!

00:00:28.554 --> 00:00:30.545
First, I get a bullshit assignment...

00:00:30.591 --> 00:00:32.422
now, Mr. Rice-A-Roni...

00:00:34.094 --> 00:00:35.584
don’t even speak American.

00:00:36.764 --> 00:00:38.755
Come on. My ride’s over here.
